OL,3,C'Major power issue' shuts down entire
OL,4,CWest Midlands Metro network
OL,6,FA 'major power failure' has brought
OL,7,Fthe entire West Midlands Metro network
OL,8,Fto a halt, with no trams running
OL,9,Fbetween Birmingham and Wolverhampton.
OL,11,FThe issue was first announced at 11:32
OL,12,Fon Tuesday 12 May on its X (formerly
OL,13,FTwitter) account.
OL,15,FIt means no trams are running at all
OL,16,Fbetween Birmingham and Wolverhampton.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/3
