OL,3,C'Major power issue' shuts down entire
OL,4,CWest Midlands Metro network
OL,6,FWest Midlands Metro is currently
OL,7,Fissuing updates on social media, and
OL,8,Fsays it is unable to make
OL,9,Fannouncements or, or update
OL,10,Finformation boards because of the
OL,11,Fissue.
OL,13,FIn a statement passengers have been
OL,14,Ftold: "Tickets and passes are being
OL,15,Faccepted on National Express buses,
OL,16,Fand West Midlands Trains from
OL,17,FWolverhampton to Birmingham."
